  <span class="italic">market</span>-
  <span class="italic">based</span> rate of time preference, and a much lower or zero long-run discount rate, which we associate with an 
  <span class="italic">ethical</span> rate of time preference.
  <a ref-type="fn" rid="Fn13" href="#Fn13">13</a>
 </p>
